videos.description: Eli Brooks misses a 3-pointer, but Jon Teske is able to tip the ball in to give Michigan a 36-25 lead over Gonzaga at the half.

videos.headline: Teske tips it in for Michigan to end first half

videos.description: Zavier Simpson misses his layup attempt, but Jon Teske is there to put in the dunk.

videos.headline: Teske's putback dunk pads Michigan's lead
